These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, traveling, card-games, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, zombie, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, rowing, basketball, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, boat, tram, quad-bike
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##8
 2. the person driving the scooter is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
 5. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 8. the person watching western movies is between the person driving the boat and the person who's sport is rowing##2
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
13. the person watching zombie movies is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
14. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person driving the tram##1
15. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the person who's sport is rowing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | hiking     | traveling   | filmmaking | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | western   | adventure   | zombie  |
| Sport         | rowing  | basketball  | badminton  | baseball |
| Transport     | scooter    | tram | boat     | quad-bike    |

