.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, coffee, cola
There 4 different types of food: potato, strawberry, apricot, cherry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, dubstep, electronic
4 different pets are kept: pony, horse, bird, rat
 1. the fan of dubstep is between the owner of the pony and the fan of hip-hop##2
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 4. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8
 5. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the fan of hip-hop##8
 6. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
 7. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
 8. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of funk is the owner of the horse##1
10. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
11. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
12. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5
14. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
15. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person eating potato##1
17. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the fan of hip-hop##8
18. the person eating strawberry is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
19. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | fanta | coffee | cola  | almond-milk  |
| Food          | cherry     | strawberry | potato | apricot  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | dubstep  | electronic | funk |
| Pet           | bird | rat | pony    | horse  |

