.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, chess, photography, board-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, sports, thriller, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, soul, gospel, salsa
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, skateboarding, badminton, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the fan of punk##5
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person watching epic movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8
 7. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
10. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
11. the person watching epic movies is not to the left of the fan of soul##8
12. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
