.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, eggplant, grapes, blueberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, hiking, woodworking, magic-tricks
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, chef, architect, nurse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, soccer, badminton
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the firefighter##6
 2. the nurse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 3. the person eating blueberry is the architect##1
 4. the person eating eggplant is between the firefighter and the chef##2
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the right of the person eating eggplant##8
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the nurse##1
10. the chef is the person who's sport is baseball##1
11. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the right of the person eating zucchini##8
12. the firefighter is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the chef is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
15. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
