 9. the italian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
11. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person watching sports movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
13. the french is not to the right of the person watching sports movies##8
