 7. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##8
 8. the person driving the van is somewhere between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7
 9. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
10. the engineer is not to the left of the engineer##8
11. the security-guard is on the far left##1
12. the analyst is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
14. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
15. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
