The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, electronic, classical, country
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, water-polo, parkour
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, trike, jet-ski
 1. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 4. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 8. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##8
 9. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the fan of electronic##8
11. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of classical is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola   | hot-chocolate     | lemonade    | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | country      | classical     | electronic     |
| Sport         | surfing | water-polo  | parkour     | cricket  |
| Transport     | tram     | trike | jet-ski | motorbike     |

